# REPLICATION-NOTES — ARCHIVED 2026-04-10

The original REPLICATION-NOTES.md described setup steps that predate the
recovery plan and do not reflect the current repo structure, grammar build
process, or ticket-based pipeline.

## Status

NOT YET WRITTEN — this document will be authored after Phase 1 completes
and the pipeline produces its first verified Python stub from a real VistA routine.

A correct replication guide requires:
  - Confirmed working grammar build on Linux + macOS
  - Confirmed working requirements.txt install
  - Confirmed BOOT-T01 through VISTA-T01 all closing successfully
  - Confirmed model/harness agnosticism verified on at least 2 different executors

Do not attempt replication from this document. Use README.md instead.
